title: Rumble or Kennen?
body: I can not choose please help. D: {{champion:85}} or {{champion:68}}

replies.body:
rumble = most difficult champion in game
kennen = is not as difficult and is more meta this season
Both are good and have the same role. Kennen has more a better laning phase than Rumble, but Kennen is also a higher risk champion in teamfights.
